  "instructions": [
    "Cook the vermicelli rice noodles according to package instructions and set aside.",
    "Melt the butter in a large ttukbaegi earthenware pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, ground cumin, and cayenne pepper. Cook, stirring constantly, for 1 minute.",
    "Add the flour and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Gradually add the chicken broth, whisking continuously, and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and add the heavy cream, Dijon mustard, salt, and black pepper. Stir until the sauce thickens.",
    "Add the cooked noodles to the pot and toss to coat with the sauce.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, until the noodles are well coated.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley before serving.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
